 thermal capture cross section, 312 b, in ENDF/B-VII.0. To re-    6331 1451
 solve this discrepancy, it was necessary to stipulate a 2200 m/s 6331 1451
 capture cross section of 358 b.  The parameters of the           6331 1451
 determined to invoked bound level in ENDF/B-VII.0 was            6331 1451
 reproduce this thermal capture cross section, as well as         6331 1451
 an accurately measured bound coherent scattering length,         6331 1451
 8.22-+0.13 fm [Mu06].                                            6331 1451
